Data processing
======================================================

R packages:

- `maptools`: creating map

- `ggplot2`: generating plots

- `dplyr`: adding/deleting columns

- `lubridate`: handling dates

- `car`: replacing names (in English)

- `R.utils`: saving as csv.gz

